HEADWORD: Bottomless
<hw>Bot"tom*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without a bottom; hence,
fathomless; baseless; <as>as, a <ex>bottomless</ex> abyss</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Bottomless</xex> speculations.⟦rdquo⟧
